reviews.text: One of the most renowned fast food chain in HK.

If you want to find seat during lunch time at the Laguna Plaza and to have something reasonably good at the fast food standard, here is not a bad choice. I come here for the hot clay pot rice with fish maw, chicken and minced pork at HK$48 from time to time. I believe the relatively fewer customers here has something to do with its location as it is situated on the 2nd floor!
